<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.5">
<l>collāy paiṅkiḷiyē</l>
<l>cuṭarāḻi valaṉuyartta</l>
<l>mallār tōḷvaṭa vēṅkaṭa vaṉvarac</l>
<l>collāy paiṅkiḷiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tell [him], green parakeet;</l>
<l>The one of northern Vēṅkaṭa with a wrestler-like arm</l>
<l>That raises the shining disc at his right,</l>
<l>Tell [him] to come, green parakeet!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
